Thanks so much...!

Thanks to Natsuba-san's plan, we've had a smooth
journey all the way to the live!

With respect to the completed schedule,
"It's... done...!" is what it says...

So, this secret base deserves the same treatment,
doesn't it?

I'll show respect by tidying up... my room,
Juri-chan's room, and everyone's dorm room too!

Yes... Let's tidy up...
respectfully... and put everything away...

A good retreat...
is just as important... as a good battle...

I agree, Rinze.
It's all about applying Sun Tzu's teachings.

The true success of the live will be determined
by how well we clean up now. It's time to show our spirit.

Alright everyone! Let's aim to leave it
cleaner than when we found it!
Yeah! / Yeah! /Yeah! / Yea-...!

-The poster boards and tape have all
been cleared away!

-The secret base canopy has been removed
completely!

-The secret base walls have been cleared
away and organized as recyclables.

The secret base floor...
has been swept and cleaned thoroughly.

Great job, everyone.
I've confirmed that everything is in order.

Well then... as of now,
this area will be returned to the agency.

The secret base of Houkura...
has been dismantled!
Thank you very much!

Good work! / Good work! / Good work! /
Good work... / Good work!
